<br>
Multiple warriors are needed when:<br>
<br>
a) There's a risk that the primary warrior will die (in which case you need another warrior to step up and take his place)<br>
b) The fight lasts longer than 3 minutes (because defensive disc lasts three minutes, after which time you have to swap to another warrior who can then use his / her defensive disc)<br>
<br>
Shackleton<br>
