I am a 65 Warrior. I have almost all my Ornate Armor. Pretty well equipped. But, our class is the worst balanced class of them all. Nobody wants to be a warrior. It is hard for us to hold aggro unless you have a blade of Carnage or some Hate item like that. Well, hard to hold against Pallies or SK's, actually most classes can out Aggro a warrior, they just hold back the spells till we pummell the mob a few pct. Then they might feel safe. On our server, we do have a few 65 warriors, but again, i know about 10 or so of them. And they are in the high end raiding Guilds. And Yes, Warriors can solo if they have the time and patience. But only up to about 51. After that, good luck. Everything else needs a slower at the higher levels. And the best damn Skill of a warrior Is /disc defensive. That is probably one of the best in the game to keep a party alive (again, if the Warrior has aggro). We do decent dmg but not what we should do. I usually crit in the 500's and crip for 900 when berserk. Well, nice telling ya what i think, that is why warriors are not so abundant. Well and at least now you know another 65 warrior to add to your list. See ya friends.<br>
